<!-- FEATURE IMAGES -->
<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:85vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2022/08/22/1_20220822154717A025.jpg" alt="X35 Exterior"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3>Compact Urban SUV</h3><p>The X35 leads the fashion trend with its dynamic design. LED headlights and daytime running lights standard across all trims. Roof rack and 16"/17" alloy wheels complete the sporty look.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-side"><div class="feature-side-img"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2022/08/22/2_20220822154726A026.jpg" alt="Interior"></div><div class="feature-side-content"><h3>Smart Interior</h3><p>8-inch touchscreen with mobile connect and Bluetooth. Multi-function steering wheel with audio and cruise controls. USB charging, pointer instrument panel, and front central armrest for daily convenience.</p></div></div></section>

<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:80vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2023/06/16/X35-3_20230616104617A171.jpg" alt="Dashboard"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3>Three Powertrain Options</h3><p>Choose from 1.5T+6MT (110kW, 210N&middot;m), 1.5T+CVT for effortless driving, or efficient 1.5L+5MT (85kW, 148N&middot;m). MacPherson front and H torsion beam rear suspension. EPB electronic parking brake standard.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-duo"><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2023/06/16/X35-4_20230616104249A185.jpg" alt="Detail"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4>Safety First</h4><p>ESP, ABS+EBD, EBA, TCS, HHC, TPMS, dual airbags + side airbags standard</p></div></div><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2023/02/13/X35-1_20230213162139A116.jpg" alt="Wheels"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4>16"/17" Alloy Wheels</h4><p>205/60 R16 standard, 215/50 R17 double color on Premium trims</p></div></div></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-side" style="direction:rtl"><div class="feature-side-img" style="direction:ltr"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2023/02/13/X35-2_20230213162150A117.jpg" alt="Comfort"></div><div class="feature-side-content" style="direction:ltr"><h3>Versatile Space</h3><p>390L luggage volume with rear seat 4/6 foldable. Panoramic sunroof on Premium trims, standard sunroof on Honor. Air conditioning with micro filter and rear seat outlets across all configurations.</p></div></div></section>

<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:70vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2022/08/22/7_20220822154816A028.jpg" alt="Rear"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3>Available in Four Colors</h3><p>White, Brown, Red, and Blue body colors. Engine cover and bottom fender available on higher trims for a more refined look.</p></div></section>

